channel.description:
Hello guys Welcome to TyScape, I know that name sounds dumb Im changing it :) If you would like to come play and have some fun Just click ---- https://www.dropbox.com/s/o6obyi82ksouv1x/Client.jar?dl=0 ------- WARNING!" When you download it for some reason it says error cache not there or something well it is give it about 5-10 seconds and it will start downloading :)
Features- Dicing - Vote store - Curse prayer - Players shop - Donator island - All Tzhaar waves - 100% Lamp System - Custom quest tab - Bank slots - Vote4Cash system - Money pouch - 317 Gameframe - Multiple custom item - Clan chat + Lootshare - Donator Credits system - Staff interface options - summoning system - Perfect skillcape emotes - All 25 skill work perfectly - Perfect combat + perfect PVP - Dungeoneering & Pk'ing skills - Skillcape shop - Quest cape - Christmas craker - Loyalty titles system - Donator cape
Minigames - Barrows - Duel arena - Tzhaar cave - Pest control - Warriors guild
Bosses - Godwars - Corporal beast - Dagannoth kings - Tormented demons - King black dragon - Much More!
